#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:2
msgid "IC 引脚检测 2D v2（Lead 2D v2，基于颜色比例）"
msgstr "IC Lead Inspection 2D v2 (Color-ratio Based)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:6
msgid "将引脚区域划分为焊料、焊盘、引脚尖端三类子区域，分别用颜色范围二值化并计算有效比例，再结合均值/邻域统计对桥接、翘脚等缺陷做鲁棒判定。"
msgstr ""
"Splits the lead region into three sub-zones — Solder, Pad, and Tip — "
"binarizes each with its own color range to compute valid ratios, then "
"combines mean/neighbor statistics for robust detection of solder bridges "
"and lifted leads."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the "
"tool's parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:14
msgid ""
"**核心思路**：将引脚区域划分为 **焊料（Solder）/ 焊盘（Pad）/ 引脚尖端（Tip）** "
"三类子区域，分别用颜色范围二值化并计算有效比例，再结合 **均值 / 邻域** 统计对桥接、翘脚（Lifted Lead）等缺陷做鲁棒判定。"
msgstr ""
"**Core idea**: split the lead area into three sub-zones — **Solder**, "
"**Pad**, and **Tip** — and binarize each with its own color range to "
"obtain valid ratios. Combine those with **mean / neighbor** statistics "
"for robust detection of solder bridges and lifted leads."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:17
msgid "区域划分：上 = **焊盘区（Pad，橙色框）**，下 = **引脚尖端（Tip，红色框）**，中间 = **焊料区（Solder）**。"
msgstr ""
"Zone layout: top = **Pad** (orange box), bottom = **Tip** (red box), "
"middle = **Solder**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst
msgid "V2区域划分与子ROI"
msgstr "v2 zone split and sub-ROIs"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:23
msgid "**通用参数**"
msgstr "**General parameters**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst
msgid "V2通用参数"
msgstr "v2 general parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:29
msgid ""
"**焊盘长度 (像素)（Pad Length / ext_top）/ 引脚长度 (像素)（Lead Length / "
"ext_bottom）**：沿引脚法线方向向上 / 向下扩展 ROI，使其完整覆盖焊盘与引脚区域。可手动输入或在窗口中拖拽调整。"
msgstr ""
"**Pad Length (pixels) / Lead Length (pixels)** (``ext_top`` / "
"``ext_bottom``): extend the ROI up and down along the lead's normal "
"direction so it fully covers the pad and the lead. Enter a value "
"directly, or drag on the canvas."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:30
msgid "**引脚尖端长度 (像素)（Tip Length）**：引脚末端 Tip 子区域的长度。"
msgstr ""
"**Tip Length (pixels)**: length of the Tip sub-zone at the end of each "
"lead."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:31
msgid "**引脚数量（Lead Count）/ 引脚宽度 (mm)（Lead Width）**：在 ROI 内自动均分生成子框并与实体引脚对齐。"
msgstr ""
"**Lead Count / Lead Width (mm)**: divide the ROI into equal sub-frames "
"that align with the physical leads."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:32
msgid "**引脚角度（Lead Angle）**：引脚相对 ROI 的方向角。"
msgstr "**Lead Angle**: lead direction relative to the ROI."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:33
msgid "**桥接宽度 (mm)（Bridge Width (mm)）**：相邻引脚间桥接检测带的绝对宽度（毫米）。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Width (mm)**: absolute width of the bridge-detection band "
"between adjacent leads, in millimeters."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:34
msgid "**间隙宽度 (%)（Gap Width）**：相邻引脚间桥接检测带宽度（按间隙百分比），居中裁剪以减少引脚边缘干扰。"
msgstr ""
"**Gap Width (%)**: bridge-detection band width expressed as a percentage "
"of the lead gap, centered between the leads to reduce edge interference."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:35
msgid "**引脚忽略列表 / 桥接忽略列表**：选择不参与检测的引脚 / 桥接（从左到右编号）。"
msgstr ""
"**Lead Ignore List / Bridge Ignore List**: leads or bridges to exclude "
"from inspection (numbered left to right)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:36
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示各子区域二值化结果与比例统计（仅建议调试时开启）。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable Visualization**: displays the per-zone binarization and ratio "
"statistics. Recommended only while tuning."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:37
msgid "**使用共享参数（Use Shared Parameters）**：开启后，对同一组件下所有同类型引脚特征共用一套参数；关闭后可对单个特征单独调参。"
msgstr ""
"**Use Shared Parameters**: when on, every lead feature of this type "
"within the same component shares one parameter set; turn it off to tune a"
" single feature independently."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst
msgid "V2 可视化"
msgstr "v2 visualization"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:43
msgid "**焊料 / 焊盘 / 引脚尖端的颜色范围**"
msgstr "**Solder / Pad / Tip color ranges**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst
msgid "V2焊料参数"
msgstr "v2 solder parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:49
msgid ""
"**焊料颜色范围（Solder Color Range）/ 焊盘颜色范围（Pad Color Range）/ 引脚尖端颜色范围（Tip Color"
" Range）**：分别为三类子区域配置 HSV 或三色颜色公式。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Color Range / Pad Color Range / Tip Color Range**: HSV or "
"Tricolor color formula configured independently for each of the three "
"sub-zones."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:50
msgid "**焊料 / 焊盘 / 引脚 有效比例范围（Valid Ratio Range）**：各子区域有效比例的 OK 区间。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder / Pad / Tip Valid Ratio Range**: the OK valid-ratio band for "
"each sub-zone."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:51
msgid ""
"**桥接颜色公式（Bridge Color Formula）**：选择用于间隙区连锡检测的颜色公式（如 ``2B-R-G`` "
"或三色）；选择三色时配置 **三色 X / Y / Z / A** 系数。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Color Formula**: color formula used to detect solder bridges in "
"the gap region (e.g. ``2B-R-G`` or Tricolor); when **Tricolor** is "
"chosen, configure **Tricolor X / Y / Z / A**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:52
msgid "**灵敏度（Sensitivity）**：间隙桥接颜色检测灵敏度（0–1），值越大检测范围越大。"
msgstr ""
"**Sensitivity**: sensitivity of the gap-region bridge color detection "
"(0–1). Higher values widen the band."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:53
msgid "**桥接颜色范围（Bridge Color Range）/ 桥接有效比例范围（Bridge Valid Ratio Range）**：用于连锡检测。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Color Range / Bridge Valid Ratio Range**: used by the solder-"
"bridge detection."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst
msgid "V2焊料色盘"
msgstr "v2 solder color wheel"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:59
msgid "**高级设置（Enable Advanced Settings）**"
msgstr "**Advanced Settings (Enable Advanced Settings)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:61
msgid ""
"开启 **启用高级设置（enable_advanced_solder_criteria）** 后，当某引脚的有效比例未落入其 **有效比例范围**"
" 时，会进入二次判定，结合下列阈值降低误报："
msgstr ""
"When **Enable Advanced Settings** (``enable_advanced_solder_criteria``) "
"is on and a lead's valid ratio falls outside its **Valid Ratio Range**, a"
" second pass runs to reduce false positives, using the thresholds below:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:63
msgid "**焊料平均阈值（Solder Mean Threshold）**：比较该引脚焊料有效比例与所有引脚的平均值；差异大于阈值视为正常。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Mean Threshold**: compares this lead's solder valid ratio "
"against the average across all leads; a deviation larger than the "
"threshold counts as OK."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:64
msgid "**焊料邻域阈值（Solder Neighbor Threshold）**：比较该引脚焊料有效比例与相邻引脚；差异大于阈值视为正常。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Neighbor Threshold**: compares this lead's solder valid ratio "
"against its neighbors; a deviation larger than the threshold counts as "
"OK."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:65
msgid ""
"**焊盘平均阈值（Pad Mean Threshold）/ 焊盘邻域阈值（Pad Neighbor Threshold）**：对焊盘区做同样的均值"
" / 邻域比较，用于翘脚判定。"
msgstr ""
"**Pad Mean Threshold / Pad Neighbor Threshold**: same mean and neighbor "
"comparisons applied to the Pad zone, used to decide lifted leads."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:66
msgid ""
"**最小焊料焊盘差异（Min Solder Pad Difference）**：比较同一引脚的焊料区与焊盘区；正常时焊料 > "
"焊盘，差距过小说明焊盘暴露、焊料不足，可能翘脚。"
msgstr ""
"**Min Solder–Pad Difference**: compares the solder zone against the pad "
"zone on the same lead. Normally solder > pad; too small a gap means the "
"pad is exposed and solder is insufficient — likely a lifted lead."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:67
msgid "**引脚尖端有效比例范围（Tip Valid Ratio Range）**：引脚尖端区域的 OK 比例区间。"
msgstr "**Tip Valid Ratio Range**: the OK ratio band for the Tip zone."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:68
msgid ""
"**引脚平均上限阈值（Tip Mean Upper Threshold）/ 平均下限阈值（Tip Mean Lower "
"Threshold）**：所有引脚尖端平均有效比例高于上限或低于下限时判异常。"
msgstr ""
"**Tip Mean Upper / Lower Threshold**: flags the lead set as abnormal when"
" the mean Tip valid ratio across all leads exceeds the upper limit or "
"falls below the lower limit."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:71
msgid ""
"判定流程：先检查有效比例是否在 **有效比例范围** 内，若在范围内 ⇒ OK；若超出，则进入二次判定——满足 **平均阈值** 或 "
"**邻域阈值** 任一条件 ⇒ OK，两者都不满足 ⇒ NG。"
msgstr ""
"Decision flow: first check whether the valid ratio sits inside the "
"**Valid Ratio Range**. Inside ⇒ OK. Outside ⇒ run the second pass; if "
"either the **mean threshold** or the **neighbor threshold** is satisfied "
"⇒ OK; if neither ⇒ NG."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst
msgid "V2焊盘参数"
msgstr "v2 pad parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst
msgid "V2 Tip参数"
msgstr "v2 Tip parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:82
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr "**Common questions and tips**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d_v2.rst:86
msgid "**引脚末端 / 焊盘误报**：与 v1 相同 —— 元件末端无红色时关闭 **引脚末端**；元件引脚无明显焊盘区域时关闭 **焊盘** 子检测。"
msgstr ""
"**False positives on the Tip or Pad zones**: same advice as v1 — turn off"
" the **Tip** sub-check when the lead tip has no red solder, and turn off "
"the **Pad** sub-check when the lead doesn't expose a clear pad area."

